Class AliyunOSSCopyFileTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.aliyun.oss.AliyunOSSCopyFileTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class AliyunOSSCopyFileTask
extends Object
implements Runnable
    Used by AliyunOSSFileSystem as an task that submitted to the thread pool to accelerate the copy progress. Each AliyunOSSCopyFileTask copies one file from src path to dst path
